verses.verse: Oh give <S%H3034>thanks<s%> unto <S%H3068>Jehovah<s%>; For he is <S%H2896>good<s%>; For his <S%H2617>lovingkindness<s%> endureth for <S%H5769>ever<s%>.
Oh give <S%H3034>thanks<s%> unto the <S%H430>God<s%> of <S%H430>gods<s%>; For his <S%H2617>lovingkindness<s%> endureth for <S%H5769>ever<s%>.
Oh give <S%H3034>thanks<s%> unto the <S%H113>Lord<s%> of <S%H113>lords<s%>; For his <S%H2617>lovingkindness<s%> endureth for <S%H5769>ever<s%>:
To him who alone <S%H6213>doeth<s%> <S%H1419>great<s%> <S%H6381>wonders<s%>; For his <S%H2617>lovingkindness<s%> endureth for <S%H5769>ever<s%>:
To him that by <S%H8394>understanding<s%> <S%H6213>made<s%> the <S%H8064>heavens<s%>; For his <S%H2617>lovingkindness<s%> endureth for <S%H5769>ever<s%>:
To him that spread <S%H7554>forth<s%> the <S%H776>earth<s%> above the <S%H4325>waters<s%>; For his <S%H2617>lovingkindness<s%> endureth for <S%H5769>ever<s%>:
To him that <S%H6213>made<s%> <S%H1419>great<s%> <S%H216>lights<s%>; For his <S%H2617>lovingkindness<s%> endureth for <S%H5769>ever<s%>:
The <S%H8121>sun<s%> to <S%H4475>rule<s%> by <S%H3117>day<s%>; For his <S%H2617>lovingkindness<s%> endureth for <S%H5769>ever<s%>;
The <S%H3394>moon<s%> and <S%H3556>stars<s%> to <S%H4475>rule<s%> by <S%H3915>night<s%>; For his <S%H2617>lovingkindness<s%> endureth for <S%H5769>ever<s%>:
To him that <S%H5221>smote<s%> <S%H4714>Egypt<s%> in their <S%H1060>first-born<s%>; For his <S%H2617>lovingkindness<s%> endureth for <S%H5769>ever<s%>;
And brought <S%H3318>out<s%> <S%H3478>Israel<s%> from <S%H8432>among<s%> <S%H2617>them<s%>; For his lovingkindness endureth for <S%H5769>ever<s%>;
With a <S%H2389>strong<s%> <S%H3027>hand<s%>, and with an <S%H5186>outstretched<s%> <S%H2220>arm<s%>; For his <S%H2617>lovingkindness<s%> endureth for <S%H5769>ever<s%>:
To him that <S%H1504>divided<s%> the <S%H5488>Red<s%> <S%H3220>Sea<s%> in <S%H1506>sunder<s%>; For his <S%H2617>lovingkindness<s%> endureth for <S%H5769>ever<s%>;
And made <S%H3478>Israel<s%> to pass <S%H5674>through<s%> the <S%H8432>midst<s%> of <S%H2617>it<s%>; For his lovingkindness endureth for <S%H5769>ever<s%>;
But <S%H5287>overthrew<s%> <S%H6547>Pharaoh<s%> and his <S%H2428>host<s%> in the <S%H5488>Red<s%> <S%H3220>Sea<s%>; For his <S%H2617>lovingkindness<s%> endureth for <S%H5769>ever<s%>:
To him that <S%H3212>led<s%> his <S%H5971>people<s%> through the <S%H4057>wilderness<s%>; For his <S%H2617>lovingkindness<s%> endureth for <S%H5769>ever<s%>:
To him that <S%H5221>smote<s%> <S%H1419>great<s%> <S%H4428>kings<s%>; For his <S%H2617>lovingkindness<s%> endureth for <S%H5769>ever<s%>;
And <S%H2026>slew<s%> <S%H117>famous<s%> <S%H4428>kings<s%>; For his <S%H2617>lovingkindness<s%> endureth for <S%H5769>ever<s%>:
Sihon <S%H5511><s%> <S%H4428>king<s%> of the <S%H567>Amorites<s%>; For his <S%H2617>lovingkindness<s%> endureth for <S%H5769>ever<s%>;
And <S%H5747>Og<s%> <S%H4428>king<s%> of <S%H1316>Bashan<s%>; For his <S%H2617>lovingkindness<s%> endureth for <S%H5769>ever<s%>;
And <S%H5414>gave<s%> their <S%H776>land<s%> for a <S%H5159>heritage<s%>; For his <S%H2617>lovingkindness<s%> endureth for <S%H5769>ever<s%>;
Even a <S%H5159>heritage<s%> unto <S%H3478>Israel<s%> his <S%H5650>servant<s%>; For his <S%H2617>lovingkindness<s%> endureth for <S%H5769>ever<s%>:
Who <S%H2142>remembered<s%> us in our low <S%H8216>estate<s%>; For his <S%H2617>lovingkindness<s%> endureth for <S%H5769>ever<s%>;
And hath <S%H6561>delivered<s%> us from our <S%H6862>adversaries<s%>; For his <S%H2617>lovingkindness<s%> endureth for <S%H5769>ever<s%>:
Who <S%H5414>giveth<s%> <S%H3899>food<s%> to all <S%H1320>flesh<s%>; For his <S%H2617>lovingkindness<s%> endureth for <S%H5769>ever<s%>.
Oh give <S%H3034>thanks<s%> unto the <S%H410>God<s%> of <S%H8064>heaven<s%>; For his <S%H2617>lovingkindness<s%> endureth for <S%H5769>ever<s%>.
